%h1
  Remove Testimonial
%p
  Are you sure you want to
  %strong.warning
    permanently remove
  the following testimonial?
%table#links.index{ :cellspacing => "0", :border => "0", :cellpadding => "0" }
  %tbody
    %tr.node.level-1
      %td.testimonial
        = image('testimonials/testimonial', :alt => 'testimonial-icon')
        = h @testimonial.author
- form_tag do
  %p.buttons
    %input.button{ :type => "submit", :value => "Delete Testimonial" }
    or
    = link_to 'Cancel', testimonial_index_url
